    "Name": "Kratos",
    "Details": "Created to replace the slow and poorly regarded Mars, the Kratos is a 95 ton OmniTank developed by Hells Horses scientists. Powered by a 285 XL Engine, the tank is capable of reaching speeds of 50 kph and is armoured with 17 tons of Ferro Fibrous armour. Only ever fielded by the Horses, the Kratos is the hammer used by the elite Alpha and Beta galaxies to crush any opposition they encounter. The Echo configuration is armed with an ER PPC and a UAC/10. A Gauss Rifle, 2 Streak SRM-6's and a Vehicle Flamer round out the design.\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Fusion: Expensive engine that works in a Vacuum.</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#ffcc00>Movement: 3/5 Hex: 90/150 Meters.</color></b>\n\n<color=#ffcc00><b>Armor:</b> Ferro-Fibrous (C)\n<b>Structure:</b> Structure\n<b>Values       A        S  </b>\n<b>Front</b>       400     50\n<b>Left</b>         350     50\n<b>Right</b>       350     50\n<b>Rear</b>        250     50\n<b>Turret</b>      300     50\n\n<b>Total</b>      1650    250</color>\n\n<color=#ff0000>Quirk: Main Battle Tank</color>\n\n<color=#ffcc00> Omni Vehicle</color>",
